      <title>Happy Vijayadashami 2024</title>
      <link>/wiaposts/Happy-Vijayadashami-2024/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:33:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/wiaposts/Happy-Vijayadashami-2024/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/wiapost/5271-Happy-Vijaydashmi-2024.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Happy Vijayadashami 2024&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Happy Vijayadashami 2024 
    &lt;div id=&#34;happy-vijayadashami-2024&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#happy-vijayadashami-2024&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hindus celebrate Durga Puja and remember the stories of Goddess Durga fighting and defeating demons. This festival is celebrated for nine days, culminating on the 10th day, known as Vijayadashami.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;During these nine days, we recite the &lt;em&gt;Durga Saptashati&lt;/em&gt;, which consists of 13 chapters. In the first 10 chapters, various demons are vanquished by Goddess Durga.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>विजयादशमी 2024 की हार्दिक शुभकामनाएँ</title>
